    <!-- Confidentiality Agreement -->
    <template id="confidentiality_agreement">
        <t t-call="web.html_container">
            <t t-foreach="docs" t-as="doc">
                <t t-call="ibas_hris.ibas_external_layout_boxed2">
                    <div class="page">
                        <link href="/ibas_hris/static/css/ibas.css"
                                rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"/>
                        <p style="text-align: center;"><strong>CONFIDENTIALITY AGREEMENT</strong></p>
                        <p> This agreement is made and executed by and between NDM Sanchez Builders and Development Corporation; 
                        the Company and <strong><span t-field="doc.last_name"/></strong> <strong><span t-field="doc.first_name"/></strong>, 
                        <strong><span t-field="doc.job_id"/></strong>; the employee;</p>
                        <p>In that during the course of employment with the Company, 
                        the employee is subject to this Confidentiality Agreement.</p>

                        <p>
                         Employee shall not disclose CONFIDENTIAL INFORMATION to third parties nor use CONFIDENTIAL INFORMATION 
                         for any purposes whatsoever except for the purpose of performing services on behalf of the Company or for 
                         performing necessary activities on the job.  CONFIDENTIAL INFORMATION means all Company or client supplied materials 
                         and all non-public materials received from and/or pertaining to the business of the Company and/or clients including 
                         the following:
                        </p>
                        <br/>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Communications – written such as e-mail messages and faxes especially from clients,
                             reports as well as verbal messages</li>
                            <li>Project names</li>
                            <li>Client Information</li>
                            <li>Systems and Project Design</li>
                            <li>Pricing and Volume</li>
                            <li>Prospective and Existing Customer List</li>
                            <li>Business Development and Marketing Directions</li>
                            <li>Financial Data</li>
                            <li>Accounting Data</li>
                            <li>Cost and Pricing Formulas</li>
                            <li>Tax Matters/Situation</li>
                            <li>Corporate/Customer/Supplier Contract Terms/Conditions</li>
                            <li>Corporate Policies and Procedures</li>
                            <li>Legal Matters   </li>
                            <li>Corporate Background Data</li>
                            <li>Minutes of Board Meetings</li>
                            <li>Payroll</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p> Any breach or violation of this Confidentiality Agreement may result to termination of employment with the 
                            Company and possible prosecution under the following provisions of the Company’s Code of Conduct:
                        </p>
                        <br/>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Willfully divulging, releasing or giving out Company’s confidential information or records to unauthorized persons.</li>
                            <li>Unauthorized disclosure of production, business or trade secrets.</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>Please acknowledge receipt and signify conformity.</p>
                        <br/>
                        <br/>
                        <br/>
                        <br/>
                        

                        <table style="width: 100%;">
                            <tr style="text-align: center;">
                                <td><span class="uppercase" t-field="doc.first_name"/> <span class="uppercase" t-field="doc.last_name"/></td>
